.TH PO-DIFF 1 "February 2026" "po-diff 1.0.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
po-diff \- compare PO/TS translation files
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B po-diff
[\fIOPTIONS\fR] \fIOLD_FILE\fR \fINEW_FILE\fR
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B po-diff
compares two gettext .po or Qt .ts translation files and shows the differences between them. It identifies added, removed, and modified translations, as well as changes to fuzzy status.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-f ", " \-\-format " " \fIFORMAT\fR
Output format. Valid values are:
.RS
.IP \fBtext\fR
Plain text output (default)
.IP \fBjson\fR
JSON output for programmatic processing
.IP \fBhtml\fR
HTML report with styling
.RE
.TP
.BR \-o ", " \-\-output " " \fIFILE\fR
Save the report to FILE instead of printing to stdout.
.TP
.BR \-h ", " \-\-help
Show help message and exit.
.TP
.BR \-v ", " \-\-version
Show version number and exit.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
No differences found between the files.
.TP
.B 1
Differences were found, or an error occurred.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
Compare two PO files:
.B po-diff old.po new.po
.TP
Generate an HTML report:
.B po-diff -f html -o diff.html old.po new.po
.TP
Output as JSON:
.B po-diff -f json old.po new.po > changes.json
